60
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,333
Don't be nervous!

61
00:04:36,333 --> 00:04:37,900
Who is nervous?

62
00:04:39,867 --> 00:04:40,800
Hey, Xiao Yu.

63
00:04:41,067 --> 00:04:42,700
It's on the other side.

64
00:05:04,867 --> 00:05:05,867
In the name of the Grand Supreme Elderly Lord,

65
00:05:05,967 --> 00:05:07,367
I command you!

66
00:05:07,633 --> 00:05:09,167
Grandpa, I'm back!

67
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,267
Welcome back!

68
00:05:15,367 --> 00:05:16,167
Yes.

69
00:05:16,567 --> 00:05:18,767
