71
00:05:20,767 --> 00:05:21,700
Exorcism?

72
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,500
For the dog?

73
00:05:27,467 --> 00:05:28,600
Hello.

74
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,367
Recalling his frightened soul.

75
00:05:31,467 --> 00:05:32,233
Ready?

76
00:05:32,367 --> 00:05:33,233
Ok, thank you.

77
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,567
No problem.

78
00:05:35,467 --> 00:05:36,167
Thank you.

79
00:05:36,333 --> 00:05:37,167
Take care.

80
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:38,667
Thanks.

81
00:05:45,133 --> 00:05:46,333
This is...?

82
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,367
Grandpa, allow me to introduce you,

83
00:05:48,467 --> 00:05:50,167
